WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.820 --> 00:00:03.460
It’s a behind story about how HaSeul became the third member of LOONA!!!

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:05.160
‘To be honeset, it doesn’t feel real that I’ve become the third member’

00:00:05.620 --> 00:00:07.340
‘I always... practiced dancing and singing until midnight’

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:10.340
‘to get a good score in a group performance test...’

00:00:10.340 --> 00:00:12.320
‘But I missed two parts of choreography in the test...’

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:14.160
‘after the test finished, I came out the test room... and cried!’

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:17.140
'Because I thought I can’t be the new member of LOONA’

00:00:17.140 --> 00:00:20.180
‘Friends helped me calm down and said it’ll be alright’

00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:22.600
'But... when I went back to the test room'

00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:25.640
'The manager said… 'we made a decision. The new member is HaSeul’'

00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:27.420
'I couldn’t stop crying after I heard that!!'

00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:33.060
HaSeul cried a lot when she heard the news she is the third member of LOONA

00:00:33.240 --> 00:00:35.500
‘I can’t forget that moment...really…’

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:38.080
‘It was a kind of stunning moment for me!!!’

